00:36:20,216 --> 00:36:22,009
Tapi, dia bukan arwah?

446
00:36:25,262 --> 00:36:27,139
Aduh, panas sekali.

447
00:36:27,223 --> 00:36:28,474
Siapa kau?

448
00:36:29,183 --> 00:36:30,684
