- Yu-ri?

449
00:36:30,768 --> 00:36:32,895
Kau tak tahu? Kau mengenalku.

450
00:36:32,978 --> 00:36:34,355
- Yu-ri?
- Yu-ri?

451
00:36:34,855 --> 00:36:36,649
Yu-ri!

