462
00:37:05,469 --> 00:37:06,595
Ikuti aku.

463
00:37:08,889 --> 00:37:09,890
Astaga.

464
00:37:11,976 --> 00:37:12,977
<i>Anak laki-laki?</i>

465
00:37:13,477 --> 00:37:15,479
